OL,3,CThe Good Life star Dame Penelope Keith
OL,4,Cdies aged 86
OL,6,FDame Penelope Keith has died aged 86
OL,7,Fafter being diagnosed with cancer, her
OL,8,Ffamily announced.
OL,10,FThe legendary TV actress was best
OL,11,Fknown for her roles a snobbish
OL,12,Fsuburbanite Margo Leadbetter in
OL,13,Fclassic British sitcom The Good Life,
OL,14,Fwhich launched in 1975, and the
OL,15,Fwidowed aristocrat Audrey fforbes-
OL,16,FHamilton, which first aired in 1979.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
