OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782800290
OL,3,CThe Good Life star Dame Penelope Keith
OL,4,Cdies aged 86
OL,6,FIn a statement, her family said: "We
OL,7,Fare deeply saddened to announce that
OL,8,FDame Penelope Keith died peacefully
OL,9,Fwhilst living with cancer at her home
OL,10,Fin Surrey where she had lived for more
OL,11,Fthan 50 years.
OL,13,F"The family is grateful for the care
OL,14,Fand support she received throughout
OL,15,Fher treatments, and ask that their
OL,16,Fprivacy be respected at this time."
