OL,3,CThe Good Life star Dame Penelope Keith
OL,4,Cdies aged 86
OL,6,FDame Penelope started her career on
OL,7,Fthe stage and joined the Royal
OL,8,FShakespeare Company in 1963 but became
OL,9,Fa household name for her work in
OL,10,Fsitcoms.
OL,12,FShe won a Bafta in 1977 for playing
OL,13,FMargo, the snobbish bullying social
OL,14,Fclimber, but later reveals a heart of
OL,15,Fgold.
OL,17,FThe Good Life followed couple Tom and
OL,18,FBarbara Good, played by Richard Briers
OL,19,Fand Felicity Kendal, who try to escape
OL,20,Fthe rat race in their suburban house
OL,21,Fin Surbiton.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
