OL,3,CThe Good Life star Dame Penelope Keith
OL,4,Cdies aged 86
OL,6,FThey try to become self-sufficient,
OL,7,Fturning their gardens into an
OL,8,Fallotment and introducing farmyard
OL,9,Fanimals, much to the horror of their
OL,10,Fneighbours ` Margo and her husband
OL,11,FJerry.
OL,13,FIn the first episode she was heard but
OL,14,Fnot seen, but her presence increased
OL,15,Fas the show went on.
OL,17,FIn the BBC sitcom To The Manor Born,
OL,18,FDame Penelope's character Audrey is
OL,19,Fforced to sell her vast country
OL,20,Festate, Grantleigh Manor, after the
OL,21,Fdeath of her husband.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
