OL,3,CThe Good Life star Dame Penelope Keith
OL,4,Cdies aged 86
OL,6,FShe moves into the estate's modest
OL,7,Flodge house but manages to keep her
OL,8,Fbutler and Rolls-Royce.
OL,10,FFrom the lodge she can keep an eye on
OL,11,Fnew owner and nouveau riche
OL,12,Fsupermarket millionaire Richard
OL,13,FDeVere, played by Peter Bowles.
OL,15,FThe actor was a made a dame in 2014
OL,16,Ffor services to the arts and charity.
