OL,3,CThe Good Life star Dame Penelope Keith
OL,4,Cdies aged 86
OL,6,FIn a tribute posted on X, former
OL,7,Fculture secretary Sir Jeremy Hunt
OL,8,Fsaid: "Incredibly sad to hear of the
OL,9,Fpassing of Dame Penelope Keith CBE.
OL,11,F"She was a neighbour and friend where
OL,12,Fshe was dearly loved by all who knew
OL,13,Fher in Milford.
OL,15,F"She helped Britain laugh at itself,
OL,16,Fone of our best national qualities,
OL,17,Fand brought happiness to millions. RIP
OL,18,Fdear Penny."
