OL,3,CThe Good Life star Dame Penelope Keith
OL,4,Cdies aged 86
OL,6,FDame Penelope is thought to have last
OL,7,Fbeen seen in public with her husband
OL,8,FRodney Timson attending the Duchess of
OL,9,FKent's funeral at Westminster
OL,10,FCathedral last September.
